@startuml Overall_System_Use_Cases_EN
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam usecase {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
    FontSize 12
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
    BorderColor #F57F17
    FontSize 12
}
skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
    BorderColor #666666
}

left to right direction

actor "Visually Impaired\nUser\n(Primary User)" as User
actor "Guest User\n(Visitor)" as Guest
actor "System\n(Automated)" as System

package "Core Features\n(4 Use Cases)" #LightBlue {
    usecase "UC1: Environment\nRecognition" as UC1
    usecase "UC2: Document &\nCurrency Reading" as UC2
    usecase "UC3: Emergency\nAssistance" as UC3
    usecase "UC4: Voice Command" as UC4
}

package "Auxiliary Features\n(4 Use Cases)" #LightGreen {
    usecase "UC5: Find Items" as UC5
    usecase "UC6: Travel Assistant" as UC6
    usecase "UC7: Instant Assistance" as UC7
    usecase "UC8: Gesture Management" as UC8
}

package "System Features\n(3 Use Cases)" #LightYellow {
    usecase "UC9: User Login/\nRegister" as UC9
    usecase "UC10: System Settings" as UC10
    usecase "UC11: Language Switch" as UC11
}

' User associations
User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC4
User --> UC5
User --> UC6
User --> UC7
User --> UC8
User --> UC9
User --> UC10
User --> UC11

' Guest associations (cannot login/register)
Guest --> UC1
Guest --> UC2
Guest --> UC3
Guest --> UC4
Guest --> UC5
Guest --> UC6
Guest --> UC7
Guest --> UC8
Guest --> UC10
Guest --> UC11

' System associations (automated processes)
System --> UC1 : Auto-detection
System --> UC2 : OCR Processing
System --> UC3 : Auto-dial
System --> UC4 : Speech Recognition

' Detailed notes for each use case
note right of UC1
  **UC1: Environment Recognition**
  Java Files:
  - RealAIDetectionActivity.java
  - ObjectDetectorHelper.java
  - YoloDetector.java
  - NightModeOptimizer.java
  - DetectionOverlayView.java
  
  Features:
  - Real-time object detection (80 COCO categories)
  - Multi-frame fusion (3-frame confirmation)
  - Night mode optimization
  - Position description (left/center/right)
  - Detection accuracy: 85-90%
  - False positive rate: 10-15%
  
  Implementation:
  - TensorFlow Lite (SSD MobileNet V1)
  - Frame processing: Every 3 frames
  - Stability filtering: 2-frame confirmation
end note

note right of UC2
  **UC2: Document & Currency Reading**
  Java Files:
  - DocumentCurrencyActivity.java
  - OCRHelper.java
  - CurrencyDetector.java
  
  Features:
  - OCR text recognition (Chinese & English)
  - Hong Kong currency recognition
  - Voice playback (full-text or line-by-line)
  - Scanning area guidance
  
  Implementation:
  - Google ML Kit Text Recognition API
  - Supports printed and handwritten text
  - Processing time: 2-3 seconds (A4 document)
end note

note right of UC3
  **UC3: Emergency Assistance**
  Java Files:
  - EmergencyManager.java
  - MainActivity.java
  - TTSManager.java
  - VibrationManager.java
  
  Features:
  - Long press 3 seconds activation
  - Direct 999 dialing (Hong Kong emergency service)
  - Voice confirmation
  - Vibration alert (emergency pattern)
  - Permission handling (fallback to dialer)
  
  Implementation:
  - Single-function design (no contact management)
  - EmergencyManager (Singleton pattern)
  - AppConstants.EMERGENCY_LONG_PRESS_DURATION_MS = 3000
end note

note right of UC4
  **UC4: Voice Command**
  Java Files:
  - VoiceCommandActivity.java
  - VoiceCommandManager.java
  - VoiceCommandBuilder.java
  - ASRManager.java
  - StreamingVoiceAI.java
  - ConversationManager.java
  - LLMClient.java
  - LLMConfig.java
  
  Features:
  - Multi-language speech recognition
  - Fuzzy matching algorithm
  - Continuous conversation mode
  - LLM integration (DeepSeek, GLM-4-Flash)
  - Sleep mode (30s silence)
  - Voice wake-up
  
  Implementation:
  - ASR Engines: Android Native, Sherpa-Onnx, FunASR
  - Multi-dimensional similarity calculation
  - Context-aware conversation management
end note

note right of UC5
  **UC5: Find Items**
  Java Files:
  - FindItemsActivity.java
  - ObjectSearchManager.java
  
  Features:
  - Mark items with image capture
  - Add item description
  - Find marked items using camera
  - Location guidance
  - Save item location to database
  
  Implementation:
  - Image feature matching
  - Local database storage
  - Real-time camera analysis
end note

note right of UC6
  **UC6: Travel Assistant**
  Java Files:
  - TravelAssistantActivity.java
  
  Features:
  - Navigation (future enhancement)
  - Traffic information (future enhancement)
  - Weather updates (future enhancement)
  - Emergency location sharing
  
  Implementation:
  - Requires third-party API integration
  - GPS location services
  - Location sharing via SMS/Message
end note

note right of UC7
  **UC7: Instant Assistance**
  Java Files:
  - InstantAssistanceActivity.java
  - VideoCallActivity.java
  
  Features:
  - Call volunteer
  - Send quick message
  - Video call support
  - Contact management
  
  Implementation:
  - Phone API integration
  - SMS API integration
  - Video call framework (future)
end note

note right of UC8
  **UC8: Gesture Management**
  Java Files:
  - GestureManagementActivity.java
  - GestureInputActivity.java
  - GestureRecognitionManager.java
  - GestureDrawView.java
  
  Features:
  - Create custom gestures
  - Draw gesture patterns on screen
  - Bind functions to gestures
  - Gesture recognition and execution
  - Manage existing gestures
  
  Implementation:
  - Touch gesture capture
  - Pattern matching algorithm
  - Function binding storage
end note

note right of UC9
  **UC9: User Login/Register**
  Java Files:
  - LoginActivity.java
  - UserManager.java
  - SplashActivity.java
  
  Features:
  - User login with credentials
  - User registration
  - Guest mode (skip registration)
  - Session management
  - User preference loading
  
  Implementation:
  - UserManager (Singleton pattern)
  - SharedPreferences for session
  - Firebase integration (future)
end note

note right of UC10
  **UC10: System Settings**
  Java Files:
  - SettingsActivity.java
  - TTSManager.java
  - VibrationManager.java
  - LocaleManager.java
  
  Features:
  - Speech parameters adjustment:
    * Speech rate: 0-200%
    * Pitch: 0-200%
    * Volume: 0-200%
  - Accessibility options:
    * Vibration feedback toggle
    * Screen reader support
    * Gesture controls
  - Settings persistence
  
  Implementation:
  - SharedPreferences storage
  - Real-time parameter application
  - Settings validation
end note

note right of UC11
  **UC11: Language Switch**
  Java Files:
  - LocaleManager.java
  - MainActivity.java
  - TTSManager.java
  - All Activity classes
  
  Features:
  - Switch between 3 languages:
    * Cantonese (廣東話)
    * Mandarin (普通話)
    * English
  - Dynamic UI update
  - TTS language synchronization
  - Language preference persistence
  
  Implementation:
  - LocaleManager (Singleton pattern)
  - Resource file switching
  - Runtime locale update
  - SharedPreferences storage
end note

note bottom
  **Total Use Cases: 11**
  - Core Features: 4 (UC1-UC4)
  - Auxiliary Features: 4 (UC5-UC8)
  - System Features: 3 (UC9-UC11)
  
  **Main Screen Functions: 7**
  1. Environment Recognition
  2. Document Assistant
  3. Voice Assistant
  4. Find Items
  5. Live Assistance
  6. Travel Assistant
  7. Gesture Management
  
  **Additional Features:**
  - Emergency Button (always accessible on main screen)
  - System Settings Button (top right)
  - Language Switch Button (top right)
  
  **File Location:**
  app/src/main/java/com/example/tonbo_app/
end note

@enduml
